? In control systems engineering, what does the Nyquist stability criterion use to determine the stability of a feedback system?
[A] The step response overshoot percentage
[B]* The number of encirclements of the critical point in the complex plane
[C] The root mean square of the system transfer function
[D] The phase margin measured at the unity gain crossover frequency
